A Gardner’s favorite clog! Waterproof rubber upper with a soft-touch moisture-absorbent lining. Easy clean outsole so no dirt in the house! Fun bright prints to make your day out in the garden that much more fun!
Package Dimensions ‏ : ‎ 11.46 x 8.19 x 3.78 inches; 1.37 Pounds
Date First Available ‏ : ‎ January 3, 2022
ASIN ‏ : ‎ B09PL6QJGT

Rubber sole
CUTE CLOGS: Embrace the outdoors this season and spend the day in the sun wearing the Western Chief Garden Clogs featuring cute waterproof clogs with a closed round toe silhouette and an upper that flaunts floral detail throughout
QUALITY MATERIAL: Our waterproof clogs feature a durable man-made rubber upper that is easy to clean along with a neoprene insulated lining and insole to keep your feet warm and dry, and a sturdy man-made rubber outsole
SLIP-ON STYLE: Slip-on construction of our Western Chief garden clogs along with the easy pull tab at the back make putting on and taking off a breeze, especially when on-the-go
STURDY SUPPORT: Durable rubber clogs highly resistant to wear and abrasion feature a rubber treaded outsole to reduce slipping and a memory foam insole for comfort and support
ALL-OVER PRINTS: Available in multiple women’s sizes in 14 various prints, from floral prints to various other colorful patterns, to add a fun touch to your outfit, our slip-on garden clogs are an ideal choice for the summer
